{"code":"#version 300 es\nprecision mediump float;\n\nin vec2 o_texCoord;\nlayout(location \u003d 0) out vec4 out_0;\n\nuniform sampler2D albedo;\nuniform vec4 diffuse; \n\nuniform vec2 mapuv;\nuniform vec2 o_tile;\nvoid main ()\n{\n    vec2 uv \u003d o_texCoord;\n  if(mapuv.x \u003e 0.0 \u0026\u0026 mapuv.y \u003e 0.0){\n   vec2 size \u003d 1.0 / mapuv;\n   vec2 offset \u003d size * o_tile;\n   uv \u003d offset + size * o_texCoord;\n   }\n   vec4 textureColor \u003d texture( albedo,uv);\n\n   out_0 \u003d diffuse * textureColor;\n}"}